{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Hold a public inquiry into treatment of care home residents during the pandemic",
        "additional_details": "Remembering my father, in care with dementia and living only for his children's visits, and on behalf of other care home residents and their loved ones throughout the country, I call for accountability.\r\n \r\nWe need to know how these restrictions - which I believe were cruel and unnecessary - were allowed to be imposed on care home residents, so that we can make sure it never happens again.\r\n",
        "background": "Over the last two years, care home residents have been isolated and denied contact with their loved ones, severely effecting their quality of life. We want a public inquiry, so that decision makers are held to account, and lessons are learned for the future.",
